column5: I got my first ski last sat and man im hooked!!!
It don't take much now does it!
Fat girl ... and cute !!!!
nice fish
So that's what a 50 looks like ?    Now I want one.     Congrats on the catch Larry.
You forgot to Grey out the parliament buildings
I thought it was a steeple and some guys will tell you that's where the best muskie fishing is so I left it in as an inside joke  guess no one got it....LOL
was gonna say...you cut out the steeples.........................
I like the pose..... and the big girl Congratulations Lungelarry Leechman
zoinks, what a brute!
Nice fish and this made me laugh pretty good.
Great fish Lungelarry.  Thats a real nice $50 Terry.  If that was my fish i would print a few of those off.
FISH of a life time!!!
Nice fish, but whats with blacking, sorry greying out the back ground and even your boat? weird
Amazing catch.  Catch, Photograph, and well usually Release.   MTBF
Nice Fish but.. has anyone ever said that you look like Bill Goldberg from WCW?
Beauty Fish, congrats  Joey
PUT HER ON THE WALL
Nice fish,,,,,  No details
Wow. Beautiful fihs.  Details?  What did you catch her on?  Good fight?
great pic.. other than the odd gray stuff happening and a great writeup:)
congratz on a very nice looking big girl I dont blame ya for keeping it to your self not every one has to be told about well maybe a lure unless its a top secret one LOL.  Cheers Mike
you could tell me where, when, how, what lure, depth, and any other possible info and i still wont get into any fish...nice job!
A Magnificant Muskie right there.....

That doesn't look like a kawartha muskie, you don't see too many of them over 50.  Beauty fish though wherever it came from.  Too bad its tail fin got all ripped up like that.  You should invest in a Beckman Pen Fin saver, money well spent IMO.  Just for curiousities sake, why the grey-out on the boat?
nice job & fish porn Larry.. all we need to know is that it was caught.
Beauty speciman right there. How FAT will she be in 4 months!!!!!
Thought I'd help out a little...
Great job on the big girl, Larry. Thanks for showing us. Congrats to you!
Very nice fish, looks like an Ottawa river ski to me.  Beauty.
I'm with Raf & Roy on this one  Awesome catch!
Nice job on the fish. Can't say the same for your Photoshop skillls........................Secret spot AND a secret boat.......
Hey, I know that spot. nice fish
An excellent fish LL!!!  ... but I think you'll catch a bigger one in that ol' farm pond you fish in  ... unless you're not going to fish anymore this year?
Beauty fish Larry!!!....keep em coming
A fine specimen of a fish Larry...  Congradz !!
Like all good porn (fish porn or otherwise) we don't watch it for the story line!  Great fish!  Little Curious George on the boat blur though? Cheating on your usual fishing buddy, my guess...
great fish! was she just 50? what's the measurement?
I can only dream....thanks for sharing that picture Larry
That is a nice fish indeed.
